{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/introduction-to-loops-in-javascript/lab-repeat-a-string/build-a-string-repeating-function","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"lab-repeat-a-string","demoType":null,"title":"Napravi funkciju koja ponavlja niz slova","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U ovoj laboratoriji, kreiraćete funkciju koja ponavlja sekvencu slova data u određeno vreme. Za potrebe ove laboratorije, nemojte koristiti metodu/način koji je ugrađen unutar <code>.repeat()</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Cilj:</strong> Popunite korisničke priče navedene ispod i prođite sve testove kako biste završili laboratorijum.</p>\n<p>Priče o korisniku:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Treba da kreiraš funkciju nazvanu <code>repeatStringNumTimes</code> koja prima dva parametra: niz znakova i broj.</li>\n<li>Funkcija treba da vrati niz znakova ponovljen navedeni broj puta.</li>\n<li>Ako je broj manji ili jednak nuli, funkcija treba da vrati prazan niz znakova.</li>\n</ol>\n</section>","id":"afcc8d540bea9ea2669306b6","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":26,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"introduction-to-loops-in-javascript","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/introduction-to-loops-in-javascript/lab-repeat-a-string/build-a-string-repeating-function"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Treba da kreiraš funkciju nazvanu <code>repeatStringNumTimes</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isFunction(repeatStringNumTimes);"},{"text":"<p><code>repeatStringNumTimes</code> Trebalo bi da primi dva parametra.</p>","testString":"assert.lengthOf(repeatStringNumTimes, 2);"},{"text":"<p>Funkcija <code>repeatStringNumTimes</code> treba da uvek vrati niz znakova.</p>","testString":"assert.isString(repeatStringNumTimes('hello', 3));"},{"text":"<p><code>repeatStringNumTimes(\"*\", 3)</code> mora vratiti niz znakova <code>***</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(repeatStringNumTimes('*', 3), '***');"},{"text":"<p><code>repeatStringNumTimes(\"abc\", 3)</code> trebalo bi da vrati sekvencu slova <code>abcabcabc</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(repeatStringNumTimes('abc', 3), 'abcabcabc');"},{"text":"<p><code>repeatStringNumTimes(\"abc\", 4)</code> trebalo bi da vrati sekvencu slova <code>abcabcabcabc</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(repeatStringNumTimes('abc', 4), 'abcabcabcabc');"},{"text":"<p><code>repeatStringNumTimes(\"abc\", 1)</code> treba da vrati niz znakova <code>abc</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(repeatStringNumTimes('abc', 1), 'abc');"},{"text":"<p><code>repeatStringNumTimes(\"*\", 8)</code> mora vratiti niz slova <code>********</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(repeatStringNumTimes('*', 8), '********');"},{"text":"<p><code>repeatStringNumTimes(\"abc\", -2)</code> mora vratiti prazan niz znakova (<code>\"\"</code>).</p>","testString":"assert.isEmpty(repeatStringNumTimes('abc', -2));"},{"text":"<p><code>repeatStringNumTimes(\"abc\", 0)</code> treba da vrati <code>\"\"</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isEmpty(repeatStringNumTimes('abc', 0));"},{"text":"<p>Putanja koja je napravljena unutar <code>repeat()</code> ne bi trebalo koristiti.</p>","testString":"assert.notMatch(__helpers.removeJSComments(code), /\\.repeat/g);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/introduction-to-loops-in-javascript/#lab-repeat-a-string","dashedName":"build-a-string-repeating-function","certification":"introduction-to-loops-in-javascript","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"introduction-to-loops-in-javascript","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"lab-repeat-a-string","isFirstStep":true,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":true,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/introduction-to-loops-in-javascript/lab-missing-letter-detector/build-a-missing-letter-detector","prevChallengePath":"/learn/introduction-to-loops-in-javascript/lab-profile-lookup/lab-profile-lookup","id":"afcc8d540bea9ea2669306b6","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":26,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function repeatStringNumTimes(str, num) {\r\n  if (num < 1) return '';\r\n  return num === 1 ? str : str + repeatStringNumTimes(str, num - 1);\r\n}\r\n\r\nrepeatStringNumTimes('abc', 3);","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/introduction-to-loops-in-javascript/lab-repeat-a-string/build-a-string-repeating-function"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}